import { OptionProductivity } from './tsx/folloze/OptionProductivity';
import { LinearArrow } from './tsx/folloze/LinearArrow';

export interface IBasicIcon {
  stroke?: string
  fill?: string
}

export const icons = {
  arrow: {
    left: ArrowLeft,
    right: ArrowRight,
    up: ArrowUp,
    down: ArrowDown,
  },
  chevron: {
    left: ChevronLeft,
    right: ChevronRight,
    up: ChevronUp,
    down: ChevronDown,
  },
  controls: {
    check: Check,
    minus: Minus,
    pause: Pause,
    play: Play,
    plus: Plus,
    stop: Stop,

  magnifier: {

    filter: Filter,

    globe: Globe,

    star: Star,
    clock: Clock

  nav: {

    productivity: Productivity,
